q_ch: 我是Advanced Sewers，请将属于我的所有2024年5月1日-2024年5月30日之间开始的裁剪任务转给Premier Sewers。
q_en: I am an Advanced Sewer. Please transfer all cutting tasks that started between May 1, 2024, and May 30, 2024, to Premier Sewers.

command: SELECT id FROM working_group WHERE name = 'Advanced Sewers';
SELECT id FROM working_group WHERE name = 'Premier Sewers';
SELECT id FROM cutting_tasks WHERE working_group_id = 'wg8' AND start_time BETWEEN '2024-05-01' AND '2024-05-30';
SELECT id FROM cutting_tasks WHERE working_group_id = 'wg9' AND start_time BETWEEN '2024-05-01' AND '2024-05-30';
UPDATE cutting_tasks SET working_group_id = 'wg8' WHERE id IN ();
UPDATE cutting_tasks SET working_group_id = 'wg9' WHERE id IN ();
